# Business Differentiation
# ========================
# HomeLinkGH payments are identified by:
# - Transaction prefix: HLG-TXN-, HLG-MOMO-, HLG-PP-
# - Redirect URL: https://homelinkgh.com/payment/callback
# - Title: "HomeLinkGH Services"
# - Description: "Service Payment"
#
# Beacon payments are identified by:
# - Transaction prefix: TXN-, MOMO-, PP-
# - Redirect URL: https://beaconnewbeginnings.org/payment/callback
# - Title: "Beacon of New Beginnings"
# - Description: "Donation"

